name: Bitcoin Drops to $86K as Asian Markets Trigger Selloff
description: The colossal Golem kneels on the lattice floor, its brass joints seizing. From eyes of cracked porcelain, the ritualistic drain begins: cyan tears of global liquidity stream out, mapping the sacred noise of entropic collapse.
